name: VASErrorCode
desc: Constants representing APDU status codes for a VAS response.

items.name: static var VASErrorCodeSuccess: NFCVASResponse.ErrorCode
items.desc: A constant indicating that the GET VAS DATA command was successful.

items.name: static var VASErrorCodeUserIntervention: NFCVASResponse.ErrorCode
items.desc: A constant indicating that the tag requires user intervention.

items.name: static var VASErrorCodeDataNotActivated: NFCVASResponse.ErrorCode
items.desc: A constant indicating that the data isn’t activated.

items.name: static var VASErrorCodeDataNotFound: NFCVASResponse.ErrorCode
items.desc: A constant indicating that data wasn’t found.

items.name: static var VASErrorCodeIncorrectData: NFCVASResponse.ErrorCode
items.desc: A constant indicating that the data is incorrect.

items.name: static var VASErrorCodeUnsupportedApplicationVersion: NFCVASResponse.ErrorCode
items.desc: A constant indicating an unsupported application version.

items.name: static var VASErrorCodeWrongLCField: NFCVASResponse.ErrorCode
items.desc: A constant indicating that the value in the Length Count field is wrong.

items.name: static var VASErrorCodeWrongParameters: NFCVASResponse.ErrorCode
items.desc: A constant indicating that VAS command parameters are wrong.
